Hi <%= @user.name.presence || "there" %>,

Your studio session is confirmed. Here are your booking details:

<% @slots.each do |slot| %>
<% et = slot.starts_at.in_time_zone(BookingMailer::TIMEZONE) %>
- <%= et.strftime("%A, %B %-d") %> from <%= et.strftime("%-I:%M %p") %> to <%= slot.ends_at.in_time_zone(BookingMailer::TIMEZONE).strftime("%-I:%M %p %Z") %>
<% end %>

Total paid: $<%= "%.2f" % @total %>

<% if @receipt %>
Stripe receipt: <%= @receipt %>

<% end %>
Studio address:
Small City Studio
<%= BookingMailer::STUDIO_ADDRESS %>

A few things to know before your session:
- Arrive a few minutes early — your session time starts when your slot begins, not when you walk in.
- Bring any instruments, cables, or gear you need.
- Basic gear and headphones are available in the studio.
- Need to cancel? Sign in and visit My Bookings to check your cancellation options.

We look forward to having you. If you have any questions, just reply to this email.

